reviewText: 2 great movies for one great price.  They are a bit dated now, but really wonderful cast members and great action.
Loved body of lies because it shows the dangers of CIA work, and three kings are is a great bonus
Great movie set  had never even heard of three Kings before and thoroughly enjoyed it  well worth buying!
The two movies together make a good bundle. The quality of one of the blue dvd is a little strange - there was no starting menu.
body of lies is an exelent movie, but three kings is not the best choice for the bundle i hope to see blod diamond or another, o a leonardo di caprios bundle, gangs of NY or others....
These are two classic films and look terrific on Blu-Ray and I could not be happier with the whole purchase...AAA+++
